name: Oelida Heshbranth
description:
Interactive portrait of fictional character Oelida Heshbranth in interactive heliantone style. Referance image is created using generative adversarial network.Click/Tap hold to interact. Swipe/Drag right/left to rotate. 
-> Oelida Heshbranth the inventor who revolutionized interstellar travel with 'Spatial Transference Drive'(aka Triquetra Drive). Died soon after her invention in a car accident. Her daughter led the team who built the engine. | @atimtay | linktr.ee/atimtakus
